Example: RNA Sequencing of Lung Cancer Samples 2021

This dataset contains RNA sequencing data from 200 lung cancer samples, including gene expression profiles and patient clinical data. It is designed to study differential gene expression and mutation burden across tumor stages.
'Cross-sectional' to compare gene expression in healthy vs. tumor tissues, or 'Time-series' to observe changes during treatment.
